      "writtenOn": "2017-07-27T19:46:01Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I didn\u0027t see anywhere the guarantees that newer devices support older feature sets. Also no where that within the same device type and family, that version n+1 is a superset of version n features.\n\nI kind of feel like we\u0027re stuck in a world where we will just need to manually be updating this when new devices and OS come out. Though it is very possible that new devices do support old feature sets in which case we won\u0027t fail immediately.",
      "parentUuid": "80792ded_38e254d4",
      "range": {
